name: Cubespace
description:
Fly through a serene cluster of spinning cubes

Use WASD to orient yourself and use the up + down keys to accelerate forward or backward.

This is my 12th game and 2nd One Game a Week project. Keep up with my weekly projects through my website at abecker.me/games and connect with me on Twitter @becker929. If you're interested in a Linux, Mac, or 32-bit Windows build, hit me up and be my guinea pig ;D
